Details - Register of penalty notices

This information about penalty notices issued is published as part of the Register of penalty notices.

Penalty notice number 3013512179
Trade name of party served
(or name of place of business)		 BARRAMUNDI TO FRIDAY
Address
(where offence occurred) 		99 BELMORE STREET TAMWORTH 2340
Council
(where offence occurred)		 TAMWORTH
Date of alleged offence
(yyyy-mm-dd) 		2010-05-04
Offence code 11370 - Carry on food business/activity without a licence - Corporation
Nature & circumstances of alleged offence

Fail to hold the required licence to carry on a food business or activity - processing & distributing seafood for sale, previous warning had been given that licence was needed
Amount of penalty $660.00
Name of party served
(with penalty notice) 		DOULIS & BLOM PTY LTD
Date penalty notice served
(yyyy-mm-dd)		 2010-08-23
Issued by NSW Food Authority
Notes

Details of this penalty notice were first published 07 Dec 2010, last updated 07 Dec 2010.

Payment of a penalty notice is not to be regarded as an admission of liability for the purpose of, nor in any way as affecting or prejudicing, any civil claim, action or proceeding arising out of the same occurrence.

People listed in the register or with an interest in a business listed can apply to add, correct or remove information if a business has been sold or disposed of after an alleged offence, or a correction needs to be made.

For information on which penalty notices are included in the register see Penalty notice publication protocol.

Users note this register is subject to change.
